<p>As you can see, I can put accordions anywhere. Here’s an accordion again.</p>

<div class="accordion">
	<div class="col is-large bp-accordion-header padding has-icons-right field has-addons is-marginless pointer">
<div class="col is-expanded is-fullwidth is-paddingless">
	<h5 class="has-text-grey-dark is-marginless"><b>JSKH:djlkfsaf"!3w452 dsafdsf423 </b></h5>
</div>
<span class="sgds-icon sgds-icon-plus is-size-4 bp-accordion-button"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="col padding bp-accordion-body">
		
<p>Hi! I’m a new accordion! You can’t make me exist using the old method. <em>is this markdown?</em></p>
<div class="accordion">
	<div class="col is-large bp-accordion-header padding has-icons-right field has-addons is-marginless pointer">
<div class="col is-expanded is-fullwidth is-paddingless">
	<h5 class="has-text-grey-dark is-marginless"><b>Accordion in accordion!!!1!111! </b></h5>
</div>
<span class="sgds-icon sgds-icon-plus is-size-4 bp-accordion-button"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="col padding bp-accordion-body">
		
<p>Lorem ipsum sit amet. <a href="https://www.google.com">Google</a></p>

	</div>
</div>


	</div>
</div>

<p>The syntax to make an accordion is:</p>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>{% accordion Title of Accordion %}
Hi! I'm a new accordion! You can't make me exist using the old method. 

**You can write everything in here using Markdown as usual!**

You can even put an accordion in an accordion!
{% endaccordion %}
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>The above yields:</p>

<div class="accordion">
	<div class="col is-large bp-accordion-header padding has-icons-right field has-addons is-marginless pointer">
<div class="col is-expanded is-fullwidth is-paddingless">
	<h5 class="has-text-grey-dark is-marginless"><b>Title of Accordion </b></h5>
</div>
<span class="sgds-icon sgds-icon-plus is-size-4 bp-accordion-button"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="col padding bp-accordion-body">
		
<p>Hi! I’m a new accordion! You can’t make me exist using the old method.</p>

<p><strong>You can write everything in here using Markdown as usual!</strong></p>

<p>You can even put an accordion in an accordion!</p>

	</div>
</div>

